_aChangeLog.text: 1-The Dustcloud now appears from Far distances
2-Added a Wall into the hallway that leads CT's to Bombsite B, to make it slower for them to reach it(The damage the wall can withstand until it breaks is a highly Changeable value)
3-Improved Ram usage and Performance by adjusting some Brush faces to "nodraw" texture
4-added some barriers on the T Side, You need to play the map to know the changes

_aLatestUpdates._sText: This is a Comeback for me in Mapping, and This is a Fast-Made Beta version, expect everything to happen, PLEASE mention these bugs or problems in the Comment Section, and it would be appreciated!

_aChangeLog.text: 1-Made the Walls in Bombsite A break on Bomb explosion
2-Solved the Fire issue in Both bombsites now the fire explosion is Visible Again
3-Added a Door in the CT's Hallway to Bombsite A
4-The door in Terroist's Hallway to Bombsite A starts Closed now
